  <title>File properties</title>

  <p>View properties of a played media by pressing the menu button in the
  top-right corner of the window and selecting <gui style="menuitem">Properties</gui>
  or <keyseq><key>Ctrl</key><key>P</key></keyseq>. They will appear on the
  <gui>Sidebar</gui> in three sections:
  </p>

      <p>Press the menu button in the top-right corner of the window and select
      <gui style="menuitem">Take Screenshot</gui>.</p>


  <terms>
    <item>
      <title><code>General</code></title>
      <p>You may find here information about the title, artist, album, year,
      duration, comment and container.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title><code>Video</code></title>
      <p>Information about dimensions, codec, framerate and bitrate.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title><code>Audio</code></title>
      <p>You may get to know about codec, channels, sample rate and bitrate.</p>
    </item>
  </terms>

